      "title": "Engaging Communication in Conflict: Systematic practice",
      "abstract": "PART ONE: BASIC COMMITMENTS Constructing Conflict Dialogue PART TWO: CONFLICT IN SMALL SYSTEMS Mediating Private Systems Working with Groups and Teams PART THREE: MOVING TO MORE COMPLEX SYSTEMS Constructing Conflict Management Systems Large Scale Interventions Working with Public Issues PART FOUR: TOWARDS BETTER SOCIAL WORLDS A Conversation with Friends"
